<HEADLINE> Malaysian Businessmen Visit Mozambique </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, April 14 (Xinhua) -- A Malaysian businessmen
delegation arrived at Mozambique's capital Maputo today for
probing the possibility of investing in the southern African
country.
</P>
<P>
Dato Wahab, the spokesman for the delegation, said at the
Maputo airport that they will meet their counterparts in
Mozambique's automaking, construction and trade sectors.
</P>
<P>
