Mozambican economy," he said.
</P>
<P>
The Malaysian delegation is expected to meet with Mozambican
President Joaquim Chissano, Mozambican Minister for Finance and
Planning Tomaz Salomao and the head of the Mozambique Bank.
</P>
<P>
The delegation will also tour the Maputo port and the Matola
industrial zone.
</P>
<P>
Egas Mussanhane, a Mozambican businessman, said the visit of
Malaysian businessmen opens new prospects for cooperation among
countries along the Indian Ocean.
</P>
<P>
The delegation will wind up its visit on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Chissano visited Malaysia late March. 
