He added he was satisfied with the speech UNITA Vice Chairman
Antonio Dembo made at the ceremony on behalf of Savimbi.
</P>
<P>
The inauguration of the government will help solve all pending
problems about the Lusaka peace accord, he said.
</P>
<P>
The UNITA members in the new government will create conditions
for Savimbi to arrive at and settle in Luanda as soon as
possible, he said.
</P>
<P>
A new U.N. Verification Mission to Angola will be set up soon
to monitor arms confiscation, mine-clearance, the forming of the
united army and the nationwide administration system, and the
definition of the status of UNITA radios, he said. 
