meeting and trade exhibition, called Medic Africa '97, started
here today with more than 150 foreign delegates and exhibitors
participating.
</P>
<P>
During the exhibition, meetings of regional laboratory
scientists, physicians on HIV/AIDS research and treatment and
experts on physiotheraphy will be held respectively.
</P>
