<HEADLINE> Guangdong Police Return Stolen Cars to Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Guangzhou, April 15 (Xinhua) -- Guangdong police returned 10
stolen cars and a stolen truck Hong Kong police at Huanggang Port
in Shenzhen this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
Guangdong police have returned at least 130 expensive stolen
cars, trucks, and luxury pleasure boats to Hong Kong since 1993.
