<HEADLINE> China, Vietnam Prefer Friendly Consultations on Nansha Islands </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 15 (Xinhua) -- Both China and Vietnam hope to
deal with the Nansha Islands issue through friendly consultations,
Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesman Shen Guofang said at a routine
press conference here today.
</P>
