100th flight under the Orderly Repatriation Program (ORP).
</P>
<P>
The majority of the returnees, comprising 47 men, 15 women,
seven boys and four girls, are from North Vietnam. Thirteen of the
returnees are from Central and South Vietnam.
</P>
