It would also train government officials involved in the
formulation, analysis, implementation and monitoring of
macro-economic and financial policies.
</P>
<P>
The first training program of WAIFEM, which will last till
April 30, would be sponsored by the Japanese government in
collaboration with IMF.
</P>
<P>
It would discuss "Macro-economic and Financial Programming and
Policies," the press release said. 
