</P>
<P>
-- France, which had been making efforts to improve relations
with Iran, was apparently embarrassed by the abrupt deterioration
of relations between Iran and the European Union, which
unexpectedly occurred last week after a German court accused
Tehran of being involved in a terrorist attack in Berlin in 1992.
</P>
