<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Pakistani Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, April 15 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Pakistani English newspapers.
</P>
<P>
The News, The Nation, The Frontier Post, The Muslim
</P>
<P>
-- India's political crisis ended Monday when the Congress (I)
party announced it would back a new multi-party coalition to avoid
fresh general elections.
</P>
<P>
The News
</P>
<P>
-- The Central Executive Committee of Pakistan People's Party
Monday decided to hold party elections at all levels, including
the post of chairperson.
</P>
<P>
