The zone is composed of a science park, which houses a dozen
research institutes, and several experiment labs.
</P>
<P>
Agronomists there will focus on the development of new wheat
strains, dry farming, water-efficient irrigation and water and
soil conservation with funds pooled by the Shaanxi Provincial
Government and departments under the State Council. 
